transcription.text:
Speaker 1: I want to cancel my next shipment from my prescription.

Speaker 2: You want to skip it?

Speaker 1: Yes, please, because I have a lot.

Speaker 2: Yes, absolutely.

Speaker 1: Do you have a new account or the last time you got a refill was in May?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: It was May last time you received it?

Speaker 2: I believe so, yes.

Speaker 1: Okay, and you want to pause, what, three more months or more?

Speaker 2: Three months, that's good.

Speaker 1: 90 days?

Speaker 2: Yes, please.

Speaker 1: Okay, next refill will be April 3rd, okay?

Speaker 2: Yes, that's fine.

Speaker 1: And you let us know, okay, if anything changes.

Speaker 2: Yes, I will. Thank you so much.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Thank you. Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.
